rComments: Super passionate prof. He clearly cares about his students. Some really well rounded lectures with different views shared from students. Learned a lot.

He's an okay prof. Assigns WAY TOO MANY READINGS! You're looking at about 80+ pages of reading /week. Lectures were boring, assignments are unnecessary and very long, and instructions and concepts are very vague.   If you don't have to take this class, don't. There are other, more interesting, classes pertaining to sexual politics and law.
teacherRatingTags: ['Tough grader', 'Get ready to read', 'So many papers']
